      • updateGeoIndexWithUrl

        boolean updateGeoIndexWithUrl(String url,
                              String createIndex)
        Calls GeoEntryIndexer.updateIndex(java.util.List<org.codice.ddf.spatial.geocoding.GeoEntry>, boolean, org.codice.ddf.spatial.geocoding.ProgressCallback) with the given URL and country code.
        Parameters:
        url - - the URL of the GeoNames server
        createIndex - - true if the index is to be created, false if the index is to be appended to
        Returns:
        true on successful execution, false when an error occurs in the GeoEntryIndexer

      • updateGeoIndexWithFilePath

        boolean updateGeoIndexWithFilePath(String fileName,
                                   String contentFolderId,
                                   String createIndex)
        Calls GeoEntryIndexer.updateIndex(java.util.List<org.codice.ddf.spatial.geocoding.GeoEntry>, boolean, org.codice.ddf.spatial.geocoding.ProgressCallback) with the given path and contentFolderId in the /content/store.
        Parameters:
        fileName - - the filename to be added to the GeoEntry index
        contentFolderId - - the path to the fileName within /content/store
        createIndex - - true if the index is to be created, false if the index is to be appended to
        Returns:
        true on successful execution, false when an error occurs in the GeoEntryIndexer
